Subject: out of bounds access on array error_text[] because of -ETIMEDOUT
 return from __send_command()
Message-ID: <38d00022-730c-948a-917c-d86382df8cb9@canonical.com>
Date:   Tue, 18 Aug 2020 13:21:00 +0100
